name: collections::btree::navigate::<impl collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Immut<'a>, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::LeafOrInternal>>::calc_length

collections::btree::navigate::<impl coll.doc:
Visits leaf nodes and internal KVs in order of ascending keys, and also
 visits internal nodes as a whole in a depth first order, meaning that
 internal nodes precede their individual KVs and their child nodes.

doc: Calculates the number of elements in a (sub)tree.
